BATTLE BORN CREW CONQUERS HOLLYWOOD AT BRAUN BATTLE OF THE YEAR U.S. QUALIFIER
Battle Born were named the newest Hollywood stars at the Avalon Hollywood in Los Angeles last night (August 20), after the Las Vegas b-boy crew stomped to victory in the Braun Battle of the Year USA qualifier (BOTY).

Judges: Easy Rock (Los Angeles), Lego (Miami) and Moy (Houston) DJs: DJ Lean Rock (Boston), DJ Renegade (London, UK) and DJ Ervin (Los Angeles)
